description: Welcome to 159 O St Unit 2—an East Side gem that is just steps from M Street Beach! This 2 bed, 2 bath condo features an open layout, modern finishes, and sunlit living spaces perfect for relaxing or entertaining. Enjoy a sleek kitchen, spacious bedrooms, and two full baths, including a primary ensuite. Step outside to your own private outdoor space and soak in the best of South Boston living. With an A+ location near Castle Island, South Boston's restaurants and shops, and easy access to the Seaport, this home truly has it all!
